---
title: SuperQuick South Indian-Style Salmon Curry with Buttery Basmati Rice
description: Take a trip to South India with this super-quick fragrant fish curry made with salmon! Served with fluffy rice and a dollop of cilantro-spiked yogurt, nothing could be more satisfying.

